Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下一個是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
